{"tid":133004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯：中共兩會建議允許香港人參軍","createTime":"2017-02-24T08:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T00:58:25.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a43499778cc7a65b0e9d045db435632c96e765","tid":133004,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:51:55.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】北京下月初舉行兩會，民建聯將提出多項建議。<br />\n<br />\n有30多名人大代表和政協委員的民建聯，建議提高港人的身分認同，包括允許港人入伍參軍，以及容許港人申請返回內地定居時毋須取消或放棄在香港的身分，又建議盡快解決高鐵一地兩檢問題。<br />\n<br />\n經濟方面，民建聯建議中央推動亞投行等金融機構，以香港為重要基地，並允許香港在絲路基金設立子基金，加強香港參與一帶一路建設。"},{"pid":"0b956deda6524902df26cdb2159096697baae4d2","tid":133004,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:52:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=211867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D211867&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8c981c0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D211867&h=3a39a65b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=211867</a>"},{"pid":"a86ba7cf4781d8f980c8e1fd53d2c747c50fc739","tid":133004,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4c9812ceee21c1205dee5dde71bbadb4f3601f","tid":133004,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20140725/large/25lp2p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140725%2Flarge%2F25lp2p1.jpg&h=15d177c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4f9ac5e6bdf5412b9179d0f8dd3503ac66821df","tid":133004,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":