圾共產黨嘅兵"},{"pid":"ae7e02cb345e31317313b6e8595ea5138cceb4a4","tid":133004,"uid":38214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉自維基<br />\n<br />\n香港和澳門兩地的《基本法》和《駐軍法》規定，《中華人民共和國兵役法》不在港澳地區實施，港澳的軍事防務，分別由中國人民解放軍駐香港部隊和中國人民解放軍駐澳門部隊負責，其成員則全數是在大陸地區招募的中國大陸公民。至於港澳當地的中國公民，<span style=\"color: red;\">則不須、也不能加入任何解放軍部隊或參與其訓練，故港澳地區既無徵兵制，亦無募兵制</span><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 不過戰爭緊急狀態例外<br />\n<br />\n其實佢邊會俾香港依啲受資本主義荼毒嘅壞份子有機會拎槍同升官 入黨籍吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係公然挑戰基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n15年葉劉已經蠢過一次 估唔到民建聯連湯都唔換就上藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c999ffe4effa5808a7b12f3494db29da79c0e18","tid":133004,"uid":5734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>轉自維基<br />\n<br />\n香港和澳門兩地的《基本法》和《駐軍法》規定，《中華人民共和國兵役法》不在港澳地區實施，港澳的軍事防務，分別由中國人民解放軍駐香港部隊和中國人民解放軍駐澳門部隊負責，其成員則全數是在大陸地區招募的中國大陸公民。至於港澳當地的中國公民，<span style=\"color: red;\">則不須、也不能加入任何解放軍部隊或參與其訓練，故港澳地區既無徵兵制，亦無募兵制</span><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 不過戰爭緊急狀態例外<br />\n<br />\n其實佢邊會俾香港依啲受資本主義荼毒嘅壞份子有機會拎槍同升官 入黨籍吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係公然挑戰基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n15年葉劉已經蠢過一次 估唔到民建聯連湯都唔換就上藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n豬一樣的隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05cc10e5e7ee9557e0707880c054d4e38ac8c26","tid":133004,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082bd2ec575e0e63dc64f76040347305ea56132d","tid":133004,"uid":6313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"唔好On9<br />\n有邊個想去送死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5697011a66d5e34c70d84d2e0657958a125c9df7","tid":133004,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民建聯帶頭參軍先<br />\n人工差距點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n民建聯先啦"},{"pid":"683969446dbb90fd092d045d2ae1d2fde19cd281","tid":133004,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇黎老解應該唔多掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪逃兵多到不能自稱百萬雄師啊</blockquote><br />\n爭崩頭就真，富裕地區仲要賄賂先有資格去。因為按規定服役滿2年，退役返鄉下當地縣級政府要接收，安排工作。而且入黨，除左讀大學最容易就係參軍。之後出左社會做嘢想加入就唔係咁容易。"},{"pid":"3a89f13adc8f02cf183fac10ce7bb4d340272265","tid":133004,"uid":15140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:11:49.000Z","msg":"依加大陸解放軍有咩福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be7b8175a2053383b8d85eca331ade31016619f","tid":133004,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:12:01.000Z","msg":"武裝起義！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c9f13491902decdfd4d44c318bd02f71c195de","tid":133004,"uid":75570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"上咗去就落唔番黎"},{"pid":"abc32b6d411acf385f81f502761dedb4bc048ec4","tid":133004,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]不如開左淘寶包郵先</blockquote><br />\n如果淘寶寄港包運費<br />\n香港零售玩撚完<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">想左好耐</span></span>[/quote<br />\n好計！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97c7b13f108674c0fd247cd50c31d8e1a27cbcd","tid":133004,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依加大陸解放軍有咩福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喺北京想食四川菜就可以揸㗎戰機飛去食呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b8e9828a1d6a74f3921d64e5902946eec00041","tid":133004,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"所謂愛國卻不熟悉國情, 有多麼人爭著當解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6751421ca6b6b78bd351f121e23eb9ac2eb45643","tid":133004,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依加大陸解放軍有咩福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喺北京想食四川菜就可以揸㗎戰機飛去食呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以合法強搶民女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f4c218dc487e04b552aa5b6db9e6ee73177260","tid":133004,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依加大陸解放軍有咩福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2014年部隊加薪，待遇有所提高，但許多基層軍官都是一個人養全家。正連職軍官月收入5000多，像楊超這樣的正團職軍官，每月工資9000多，一年下來100800塊錢是他的全部收入。"}]}